{"title":"鲁迅颂","authors":["尼扎姆"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":10,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲁迅颂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔巴基斯坦〕尼扎姆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当帝国主义的阴云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笼罩着这不幸的土地；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当封建主义的残酷肆虐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穷人死于市井和街头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无人认领、无声无息；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当老百姓受着官僚机器的压榨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地主庄园里劳作的农民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遭到皮鞭的抽打，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妻子受糟踏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女儿被扣作人质；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当鲁迅目睹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"外国老爷的屠刀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向同胞砍去……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国终于看到了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个伟大作家的崛起！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲁迅的光芒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不久即闪耀在中国地平线上！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他用如椽的大笔、火一样的诗情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"召唤人们："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为正义而战斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打碎这颠倒的乾坤！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抬起头！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱起新时代的歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在与过去不同的、光明的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新文化道路上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前进！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲁迅塑造了有名的阿Q；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他在嘲笑中哭泣："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为人类的苦难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为当权者的残忍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲁迅的著作卷帙浩繁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他唱歌，他演讲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"促人思考，点燃呆滞的心灵："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"支援历史性的长征！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"改变这腐败的秩序，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而代之以崭新的天地！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他告诫说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"延缓更替将会导致"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"慢性死亡、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更多的痛苦、牺牲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更多的悲叹、惋惜；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与其永世沉沦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不如赶快解救自己！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他吹响嘹亮的号角。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他向命运抗争。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为时光似流水，永远不待人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他向男女老少呼吁："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"停止叹息、停止流泪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把作人的尊严"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"归还给人！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我们起立"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向伟大的鲁迅致敬！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他没有死；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他虽死犹生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活在后代的心里！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔叶绍根译〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}